OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLabour MP Sir Tony Lloyd   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdies 'peacefully at home'  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sir Tony Lloyd, the Labour MP for      
OL,6, Rochdale, "died peacefully" at home on 
OL,7, Wednesday morning, his family has said 
OL,8, in a statement.                        
OL,10,FIn a post on social media, his         
OL,11,Frelatives said he was still working a  
OL,12,Ffew days before his death aged 73.     
OL,14,FThe veteran MP revealed he had an      
OL,15,Funtreatable form of leukaemia at the   
OL,16,Fweekend. He had been treated for blood 
OL,17,Fcancer and received chemotherapy.      
OL,19,FThe family described him as "our       
OL,20,Fbeloved 'Joe,' 'Dad' and 'Grandad'".   
